# W4p2 integration test: a malformed declaration alongside valid ones.
#
# The bare colon on line 4 has no valid declaration head.  The error
# recovery mechanism wraps it in an ERROR node so that the valid
# declarations on either side are still parsed and their bindings exist
# in the block.
#
# Expected behaviour:
#   - Exit code 1 (parse error is reported)
#   - Stderr mentions the file location of the bare colon (line 4)
x: 10
: bad_value
y: 20
RESULT: x
